{"tid":1084911,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"我養你啊！","createTime":"2019-03-30T18:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T00:01:06.000Z","uid":47496,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"af3caf699355a724ea218da22f5af8592dd8600d","tid":1084911,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T18:01:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7OSAI0TG-5o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7OSAI0TG-5o&d=Ru8OiKpQtXbNv5YRwinC6o5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=dd96692d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7OSAI0TG-5o</a><br />\n<br />\n4:30開始真係睇幾多次都唔會厭<br />\n雖然間隔20年但都重好感觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩首BGM配合埋星爺、栢芝嘅內心戲真係世界級<br />\n感觸原因係佢能夠完美演譯演員嘅情感「由內到外再到返內」<br />\n<br />\n20年前講「我養你啊！」女仔應該好感動<br />\n20年後講返「我養你啊！」就好似栢芝最後果句咁「你養掂自己先啦！傻仔！」<br />\n20年間嘅價值觀不經不覺已經變咗<br />\n每次睇返呢一段都好憧憬渴望有一段咁嘅姻緣<br />\n亦都好寫實咁反映返而家個社會唔容許你咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e37d7f4817ab185d918fb0345c01cc5f3540d6","tid":1084911,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e08993a03a89ea96e001cc58d2f95d8db6259c","tid":1084911,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T18:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm